r Tom ruled it out for the time being at least.\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1333, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a representative\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1283}, {\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Tom is not taking part in I am A Celeb or any TV contest shows this year,' they said.\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"A Celeb\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"any TV contest shows\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom is no stranger to reality TV - from 2013 to 2014, he was the expert mentor on Splash.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1504, \"end\": 1510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Professional_wrestling_aerial_techniques\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3203345071630353e-28, \"text\": \"Splash\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Professional_wrestling_aerial_techniques\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Professional_wrestling_aerial_techniques\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1425}, {\"ngram\": \"reality TV\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1454}, {\"ngram\": \"the expert mentor\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1500}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ITV competition series saw celebrities learn how to dive and show off the skills in a live episode.\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1516, \"end\": 1519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITV_News\", \"score\": 0.999996323465376, \"rank\": 2.3336095022585665e-06, \"text\": \"ITV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITV_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITV_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"celebrities\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"the skills\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"a live episode\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eddie 'The Eagle' Edwards, and Perri Kiely, managed to clinch the wins before the series was axed.\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1617, \"end\": 1642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eddie_the_Eagle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eddie 'The Eagle' Edwards\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4270517\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eddie_the_Eagle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eddie_the_Eagle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wins\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1687}, {\"ngram\": \"the series\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After closing the Olympics chapter of his life, Tom toldBritish Vogue: 'It feels very, very surreal.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1817, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics chapter\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1751}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt so incredibly nervous going into this, knowing it was my last Olympics.\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my last Olympics\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1895}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There was a lot of pressure and expectation.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"expectation\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was eager for it to be done\\u2026 but when I walked out, and saw my husband [Dustin Lance Black] and kids [Robbie and Phoenix] and my friends and family in the audience, I was like, you know what?\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 2137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2018, \"end\": 2036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dustin Lance Black\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my husband\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2016}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"the audience\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is exactly why I did this.\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am here, and no matter what happens in the competition itself, I am going to be happy.'\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was emotional at the end, up there on the platform, knowing it was going to be my last competitive dive,' he added.\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"the platform\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"my last competitive dive\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I have to make the decision at some point, and it feels like the right time.\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"some point\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2430}, {\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's the right time to call it a day.'\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right time\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His husband-of-six-years shared his pride on Instagram, writing: 'I am so incredibly proud of you, Tom.\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2553, \"end\": 2562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2663039828113586e-40, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His husband\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2519}, {\"ngram\": \"six-years\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2532}, {\"ngram\": \"his pride\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are an inspiration to me, our boys, and the entire world.'\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an inspiration\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2634}, {\"ngram\": \"our boys\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire world\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Potentially joining I am A Celeb is not the only thing on Tom's agenda.\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A Celeb\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2708}, {\"ngram\": \"the only thing\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2730}, {\"ngram\": \"Tom's agenda\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He provided punditry for Eurosport during the latter half of the Games and plans to continue being in front of the camera.\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2871, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"punditry\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2769}, {\"ngram\": \"Eurosport\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2783}, {\"ngram\": \"the latter half\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2806}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2819}, {\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"the camera\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While he's a famously keen knitter, Tom has also enrolled in a course at the Fashion Institute of Design and Merchandising (FIDM) in Los Angeles to add sewing to his skillset.\", \"from\": 2